Owen Wilson to be father for third time

by IANS |

Los Angeles, Sep 28 : Actor Owen Wilson, who has already two children with two different former girlfriends, is going to be a father for a third time.

According to pagesix.com, the 49-year-old star is expecting a child with Varunie Vongsvirates, 34.

Earlier, there were reports that the "Wonder" star underwent a paternity test, after a third woman came forward claiming that he was the father of her unborn child.

Now it is believed that Vongsvirates, whose LinkedIn lists her job as a business development representative for American Addiction Centres here, is that mystery woman.

Vongsvirates on Thursday shared several posts on Instagram about the pregnancy. A recent post showing her and Wilson at the premiere of his movie "Father Figures" was captioned "father figure".

When a follower asked if Owen is the father, Vonsvirates responded "Yes".

Owen fathered seven-year-old Robert Ford, born in 2011, with Jade Duell, and had his second child with personal trainer Caroline Lindqvist, who was married at the time.
